      <b data-is-speakable>To Safely Ease Social Distancing, U.S. Needs To Tackle These 5 Obstacles : Shots - Health News</b>   <b data-is-speakable>Political leaders want to reopen the economy soon, but public health experts say we first need to set up systems to prevent new flare-ups of the coronavirus. Here's what needs to get done.</b>
